    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve babyed this car since day one, and it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or door ding in sight, and the interior is absolutely flawless. It drives like a total dream! I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look\u2014I'd love to show it off to you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
