    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium upholstery remains supple and retains its original factory aroma, while the dash and trim are free of any sun fade or wear. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-backed service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched engine bay, this car is a turn-key example for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
