      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s in pristine condition inside and out. It drives so smoothly, you\u2019ll fall in love the second you get behind the wheel. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm hoping to find it a great new home quickly. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
